OL,3,CThousands of homes left without water
OL,4,Cafter burst main
OL,6,FThousands of homes in Bristol have
OL,7,Fbeen left without water or suffering
OL,8,Ffrom low water pressure following a
OL,9,Flarge burst main.
OL,11,FTwo thousand homes have had their
OL,12,Fwater supply reconnected, however two
OL,13,Fthousand six hundred households are
OL,14,Fstill being affected by the outage.
OL,16,FBristol Water said crews worked
OL,17,Fovernight and water in the network has
OL,18,Fbeen rerouted to reduce the number of
OL,19,Fcustomers affects in the BS4 and BS14
OL,20,Fareas.
