OL,3,CThousands of homes left without water
OL,4,Cafter burst main
OL,6,FThe junction of Hengrove Way and
OL,7,FHawkfield Road in the Hartcliffe area
OL,8,Fof the city is temporarily closed to
OL,9,Fallow the work to be completed safely.
OL,11,FIn a statement, the utility company
OL,12,Fsaid: "Our teams have been working
OL,13,Fhard overnight to repair a significant
OL,14,Fburst on our water main at Hawkfield
OL,15,FRoad in Hartcliffe, which has resulted
OL,16,Fin some customers being without water.
OL,18,F"There is a gas main near our pipe
OL,19,Fwhich means we have to be very careful
OL,20,Fwith our work to make sure our teams
OL,21,Fand the public remain safe.
