OL,3,CThousands of homes left without water
OL,4,Cafter burst main
OL,6,F"This, along with the need to use
OL,7,Fspecialist fittings for the repair,
OL,8,Fmeans the fix is taking longer than we
OL,9,Finitially hoped.
OL,11,F"We're sorry for the disruption and
OL,12,Fwill continue to keep customers
OL,13,Fupdated."
OL,15,FThe company also said bottled water
OL,16,Fwas delivered to its most vulnerable
OL,17,Fcustomers and a bottled water station
OL,18,Fhas been set up near the old Cineworld
OL,19,Fon Hengrove Lane which will remain
OL,20,Fopen until 10pm.
